  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>Your skill with your chosen weapon leaves opponents unable to defend themselves if you strike them when their defenses are already compromised.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Weapon Focus, Dazzling Display, base attack bonus +6, proficiency with weapon.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>Any shaken, frightened, or panicked opponent hit by you this round is flat-footed to your attacks until the end of your next turn. This includes any additional attacks you make this round.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>When you hit an opponent that has been made flat-footed to your attacks by this feat, you can spend 5 stamina points to make that opponent flat-footed to the attacks of one ally who is within 30 feet of that creature until the start of your next turn.",
